description: The Agricultural Trade domain covers detailed food and agriculture trade data: Export/Import quantity, Export/Import unit value, Export/Import Value, Trade matrix. The Trade module provides comprehensive, comparable and up-to-date annual trade statistics by country, region and economic country groups for about 600 individual food and agriculture commodities since 1961.
name: Trade Crops Livestock: Paste of Tomatoes - Lebanon
source_name: Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations
